  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And things, why it happened to the majority of the people that didn't survive, I don't know the answer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- I leave it to-- I leave it to others who are more qualified and more experienced in it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm not looking for an answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm just carry on my faith.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all I-- all I can say that I was very much conscious now that my experience, in particular and generally, the whole experience of the Holocaust has to be put-- put-- to provide the knowledge.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm very grateful for that, for the foundation of what you are acting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because this is going to be taped and stored.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I think it's very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Things are happening all over the world which is people-- people thought it should never happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's more important that the lesson of the Holocaust should be spread and taught to as far as possible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As wide a community as possible for our friends, for our nation, and for the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thank you for giving me the opportunity to tell my story.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
